---
title: Mexican Tomato Jumble with Spiced Citrus Halloumi
description: Spring is well and truly underway, with summer on the horizon! So Patrick decided to create something colourful and full of sunshine! Our delicious tomatoes from The Tomato Stall are paired with coriander and lime chicken with a hint of Mexican spice. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5723299b4dab71b6668b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/5723299b4dab71b6668b4567.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 686 kcal
  fat: 33 g
  saturated fat: 20 g
  carbohydrates: 68 g
  protein: 33 g
